  default-on/opt-out + explicit docs.
- Adding EvalResult.JudgeID + Seed touches the shared eval wire type; mitigated
  by omitempty (byte-identical pre-field output) + round-trip test as the gate.
- O(N) scan grows with eval count; acceptable v1, index deferred + documented.

